# Charts (HTML mockups)

Source of truth: @ai/rules/design/charts.md

## Quick Rules

- Chart.js via CDN only
- Colors from design-system CSS variables — no hardcoded hex
- Dark theme — grid lines and labels must contrast against dark background
- Tooltips: match card styling (rounded, blur, same border radius)
- Currency in tooltips: `UAH`, `uk-UA` formatting
- Animations on mount: staggered with other `fadeUp` elements
